{"tid":646342,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"如果Zack Snyder係詩人，Christopher Nolan係小說家","createTime":"2018-04-29T03:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T08:59:47.000Z","uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e873dad4c981b7bba4f7fb31eba48afabaa5c317","tid":646342,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"咁Steve McQueen就係當代畫家<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1723811/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt1723811%2F&d=%2B9OPQEDzr2OMqe7q0QsGlI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=70063ac6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1723811/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢拍攝既畫面用好多圖形表達，同埋場景同場景之間用大量線條指示觀眾點去睇呢個畫面，<br />\n<br />\n好似Shame一開始用男主角既裸體，係房同廳之間來回行走前後行走，形造長方形既牆身左右兩旁既空間感，同埋男主角裸體既壓迫感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/110208_31a9b83459c91b18624fc801b808e26c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F110208_31a9b83459c91b18624fc801b808e26c.png&h=857d1784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而Woody Allen就係散文作家<br />\n<br />\n佢既短篇故事篇幅短，但係內容豐富，中心主旨明確，有時候寓意深遠，令人睇完會反思同細味<br />\n<br />\n好多影評會用 嘮叨 黎形容Woody Allen電影入面既主角，久而久之好似Woody Allen先係嘮叨既人咁<br />\n<br />\n好似<br />\nMidnight in Paris 既 Owen Wilson<br />\nCafe Society 既jesse eisenberg <br />\nBlue jasmine 既 cate Blanchett<br />\nIrrational man既 Joaquin Phoenix <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/111350_1e88e1dd717defeff8a48474171827da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F111350_1e88e1dd717defeff8a48474171827da.png&h=5e94937f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7797aefabfdfdb9c917ac57f9bfb18467b7edd36","tid":646342,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁Tarantino係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=